  • TV LED Lights with Million ColorsKANTUTOE TV LED lights strip features a remarkable 16 million colors mood light, capable of generating various color atmospheres for different settings. Whether it's your bedroom, gaming room, or home theater, this TV LED lights can consistently create unique scenes and ambiances tailored to your preferences.
  • Bluetooth APP Control LED Lights for TVLED Lights for TV can be connected to a mobile app via Bluetooth. Through the mobile app, you can not only control a wide range of lighting modes but also activate the music mode, allowing the lights to synchronize and change according to the rhythm of the music.
  • Sync with Music LED TV LightsKANTUTOE LED TV lights is different from ordinary TV lights strips. It has a built-in high-sensitivity microphone, and its color can change according to the change of the music. Let you enjoy the happiness brought by music more.
  • Multi-application LED for TVLED for TV are suitable for most places such as living room, home theater, house and also for various holiday decorations such as Halloween, Christmas, etc. Extremely low heat 5V USB power supply makes the decoration safer.
  • Easy to Install TV Lights16.4ft TV lights can illuminate every side of your TV. The mini receiver can be well hidden behind your TV. Unique stronger foam adhesive and clips ensure the RGB LED light bar is better fixed on your TV.

      Unlike other TV backlights Ive tried, these are far superior because they actually adhere to the back of the TV and dont fall off after a week. The interchangeable colours allow you to change to your mood or the season. I would be avoiding the pulsing functionality unless its party time! One thing to be aware of is if your TV does automatic updates in the middle of the night the lights tend to come on with that pulse of energy, so think about this if you are planning to put them on a bedroom TV. They come on when your TV comes on so you dont have to manually put them on, but you can switch them off using the remote control if you dont want them on for whatever reason. I would highly recommend these lights. Very easy to install and they come with a suggested placement depending upon the size of your TV.
